                  <li>
                    Create your forms with Podo via Discord DM's!
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Track your submissions realtime with channel you specified.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    You can register to JotForm with Podo if you don't have an
                    account.
                  </li>
